Formula: (exists a (exists b (IsNear(b,a))) & (forall f (forall e (forall g ( IsNear(e,f) ->  IsHas(f,g))))) & (forall i (forall j (forall h ( IsHas(h,i) ->  IsNear(j,h))))) & (forall l (forall m (forall k ( IsNear(k,l) ->   IsNearby(m)))))) -> (exists c (exists a (exists d (IsHas(a,c) and IsNearby(d)))))
